          "id": "8a7f205ea60ef57b5493e30350d10b796028a143",
          "message": "fix(releaser): include !-bang breaking commits in changelog\n\nThe default conventional-commits-parser regex doesn't accept\n`type(scope)!:`, so breaking commits silently disappeared from the\nrelease PR body. Configure the parser with the conventionalcommits\npreset's header patterns so v1.0.0 syntax parses correctly.\n\nRefs: https://github.com/conventional-changelog/conventional-changelog/issues/648\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.7 (1M context) <noreply@anthropic.com>",
          "timestamp": "2026-05-02T15:32:12.836Z",
