          "id": "4539f4a9392a002e5d174ef2003c33de403ee17d",
          "message": "feat(config): reject mikrojs/* imports in mikro.config.ts (#74)\n\nDevice subpaths type-check fine in build-time config files but blow up\nat config-load with an opaque module-not-found. Add an eslint rule for\nin-editor feedback plus a regex backstop in the config loader.\n\nCo-authored-by: Claude Opus 4.7 (1M context) <noreply@anthropic.com>",
