          "distinct": true,
          "id": "18ecd6635793f0abba954f301577184acca98cb8",
          "message": "fix(repl): suspend microtasks while paused so user JS can't race deploy (#77)\n\nDraining microtasks during pause ran user .then handlers, which could\nemit MSG_LOG mid-deploy or touch the filesystem while the staged-file\nswap was in flight. Defeats the point of CMD_RUNTIME_PAUSE.\n\nCo-authored-by: Claude Opus 4.7 (1M context) <noreply@anthropic.com>",
          "timestamp": "2026-05-11T20:33:17.215Z",
