          "id": "f0ce7efcb71479ef8b44126399301b8430f49e42",
          "message": "feat(cli): quiet `mikro flash` output and show next steps (#94)\n\nStream only the latest esptool status line during flashing instead of\nthe full transcript, then surface `mikro dev` / `mikro console` as next\nsteps once the flash succeeds. Full output is still shown on failure.\n\nCo-authored-by: Claude Opus 4.7 (1M context) <noreply@anthropic.com>",
