          "id": "cf3d7551e0efbf15529e1b094577ca736095a668",
          "message": "ci(workflows): add zizmor audit and harden workflows (#107)\n\nEliminate template-injection sinks (route inputs through env), scope\nGitHub App tokens with permission-* inputs, and silence remaining\nwarnings with rationale comments. New Zizmor workflow gates main on\nhigh-severity findings; lefthook runs the same audit pre-commit when\n.github/ files are staged.\n\n---------\n\nCo-authored-by: Claude Opus 4.7 (1M context) <noreply@anthropic.com>",
